 Sally White , 28 , rescued the terrified animal from a bleak hillside where he was abandoned without food and water .
His ribs were poking through and vets feared he would not survive more than a few days .
But Sally 's love and care for the horse has turned it into a magnificent steed .
RSPCA were called in to rescue the 15.2 hands cob abandoned in a field in Swansea , South Wales .